    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, peel and finely dice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and grate (or finely chop) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and grate (or finely chop) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p>",
