    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the sauce is thickening, wash the <strong>spinach</strong>, then chop it roughly</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped spinach</strong> to the curry sauce and stir continuously for 1-2 min or until wilted</p>",
      "order": 6,
