    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lighter Goan-style basa & spinach curry</strong> over the <strong>coriander rice</strong> and garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
